body:
### headlessReader Safari Extension
This extension removes Google reader headers for a cleaner UI when you read your beloved RSS news.
Download the extension alone here: [headlessReader.safariextz](https://github.com/dingcheng/headlessReader/raw/master/headlessReader.safariextz)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
tagline: Remove google reader header for a cleaner UI
name: Headlessreader
